No. 748,

Misc.

Southerland v. Georgia. Chester E. Wallace for petitioner. Eugene Cook, Attorney General of Georgia, and Peyton S. Hawes, Jr., and Alfred L. Evans, Jr., Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

Sup. Ct. Ga. Certiorari denied without prejudice to an application for a writ of habeas corpus in the appropriate United States District Court.
